  </section>

  <!-- About -->
  <section id="about">
    <div class="section-head">
      <h3>About Us</h3>
    </div>

    <div class="about-grid-wrapper">
      <div class="about-text">
        <p>For years, we watched world-class European processing and packaging technology struggle to gain ground in Africa. The challenge was never the equipment. It was the missing local partner. PPSA was founded to close that gap with regional insight, hands-on support and a focus on long-term results.</p>
        <p>We are a family-owned company representing leading manufacturers such as Pattyn, Gerstenberg Services, API Schmidt-Bretten and Daniatech. Our work spans Sub-Saharan Africa, where clients rely on us for solutions that fit their exact needs.</p>
        <p>Our strength lies in how we operate. We learn your process, build partnerships that last, and stay involved long after installation. Clients trust us because we support them when it matters most.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Industries & Technologies -->
  <section id="industries">
    <div class="section-head"><h3>Technologies</h3></div>

    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card"><h4>Mixing & heat treatment for hygienic processing</h4><p class="muted">Advanced mixing, powder handling and heat treatment technology for dairy, beverages, food and home and personal care applications.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><h4>Processing technology for yellow fat and edible oil</h4><p class="muted">Innovative Gerstenberg crystallization and texturizing technology for margarine, shortening, ghee, spreads and related products.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><h4>Bag-in-box packaging solutions</h4><p class="muted">Pattyn automated systems integrating bag forming, filling, sealing and case packing.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><h4>Plate heat exchangers</h4><p class="muted">Schmidt plate heat exchangers for hygienic and industrial processing.</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Partners -->
  <section id="partners">
    <div class="section-head">
      <h3>Our Partners</h3>
      <p class="muted">Leading manufacturers we represent in Africa.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="partners">
      <a href="https://www.pattyn.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="partner"><img src="assets/img/partners/Pattyn_Logo.png" alt="Pattyn"></a>
      <a href="https://www.apischmidt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="partner"><img src="assets/img/partners/API_Logo.png" alt="API Schmidt-Bretten"></a>
      <a href="https://www.gerstenberg.de" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="partner"><img src="assets/img/partners/Gerstenberg_Logo.png" alt="Gerstenberg Services"></a>
      <a href="https://www.daniatech.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="partner"><img src="assets/img/partners/Daniatech_Logo.png" alt="Daniatech"></a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Regions -->
  <section id="markets">
    <div class="section-head"><h3>Regions</h3></div>

    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card"><h4>Southern Africa (SADC)</h4><p class="muted">Serving South Africa, Angola, Mozambique, Namibia, Botswana, Zimbabwe, Zambia, Malawi, Eswatini, Lesotho, Tanzania, DRC.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><h4>West Africa (ECOWAS)</h4><p class="muted">Supporting Nigeria, Ghana, Benin, Ivory Coast, Senegal, Togo, Burkina Faso and more.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><h4>East Africa (EAC & more)</h4><p class="muted">Working with Kenya, Ethiopia, Uganda, Rwanda, Burundi, Tanzania, Madagascar and surrounding regions.</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services -->
  <section id="services">
    <div class="section-head">
      <h3>Services</h3>
      <p class="muted">End-to-end support across the project lifecycle.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card"><h4>Representation</h4><p class="muted">Evaluation, feasibility, pricing and partner selection.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><h4>Training</h4><p class="muted">Operator and maintenance training with documentation and knowledge transfer.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><h4>Support & spares</h4><p class="muted">Local warranty handling, spare parts and after-sales service.</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact -->
  <section id="contact">
    <div class="section-head">
      <h3>Contact</h3>
      <p class="muted">Tell us about your requirement and we’ll set up a call.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-grid-wrapper">
      <div class="contact-grid">
        <form method="POST" action="https://formspree.io/f/your-form-id">
          <label for="name">Your name</label>
          <input id="name" name="name" type="text" required>

          <label for="company">Company</label>
          <input id="company" name="company" type="text">

          <label for="email">Email</label>
          <input id="email" name="email" type="email" required>

          <label for="message">Message</label>
          <textarea id="message" name="message" required></textarea>

          <div class="form-cta">
            <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Send enquiry</button>
            <div class="small">Or email: <a href="mailto:info@pps-africa.com">info@pps-africa.com</a></div>
          </div>
        </form>

        <aside class="card">
          <h4>Office</h4>
          <p class="small">Cape Town, South Africa</p>
          <hr>
          <h4>Emergency</h4>
          <p class="small">Phone: +27 83 676 2317</p>
          <p class="small">Email: <a href="mailto:geert.verbeemen@pps-africa.com">geert.verbeemen@pps-africa.com</a></p>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

